# Production manifest for Snakefile
# Columns: sample  KN_BC  bam_path  arrays_path
# Tab-separated, no header line, lines starting with # are ignored
#
# sample      — unique identifier for this pool/kinnex-barcode combination
# KN_BC       — Kinnex barcode (e.g. bcM0003)
# bam_path    — path to pre-Skera CCS/HiFi BAM
# arrays_path — path to arrays.txt for this pool
#
# Example:
# Pool001_bcM0003	bcM0003	/path/to/Pool001.ccs.bam	arrays/Pool001_bcM0003.txt
